sources.description: This repository is maintained by the fictions.ai team. We believe in the power of collaboration and the magic that happens when we share knowledge. Here, we'll be sharing our workflow, useful scripts, and tools related to A.I. generation.

sources.title: ChaosFlow
sources.author: BoosterCore
sources.description: ChaosFlow是一个用于展示我自己制作的一些ComfyUI工作流的代码仓库，目的是为了分享我对ComfyUI的探索和实践，同时也希望能够得到有兴趣的朋友们的反馈和建议。ChaosFlow欢迎任何水平的视觉设计爱好者浏览和评论，您也可以在GitHub上给我发消息，我很乐意与您交流和学习。
